title: Katie Armiger - Katie Armiger
description:
A very good country music CD from a very young singer. Katie definitely has promise with a clear, strong and pleasant voice. The music is good too. Country but not "twangy." Modern country that can be appreciated by fans of other genres. Hopefully Katie keeps going; she is for real.
